messages.message: Hello everyone! Good luck to us all. I'll start us off by taking this nice spot on the 6-8-11.
I'm going to branch out toward the coast. Hopefully, I can find some wheat down there!
Nice start, Alice! That 6-8-11 is a classic. I think I'll set up camp over here by the mountains—looks like there's plenty of grain to go around!
That 5-9-9 spot looks like it'll keep me fed! I'll start building my road toward the center—gotta find some clay for these bricks I'm going to need eventually.

Hey everyone! Those are some solid spots. Alice, that 6-8-11 is definitely a powerhouse, and Bob, you've got the wheat market cornered already! I think I'll settle down in the forest near that 6-brick—looks like a good place to start some construction.
Building towards the coast! That Wheat 8 looks like a great spot to aim for. Good luck with the mountains, Bob—you've certainly got the high ground for now!
